@page "/components/banner"

<TextContent>
  <Title class="pf-u-mb-md">Banner</Title>
  <Text class="pf-u-mb-md">
    A <strong>banner</strong> is a one-line, full color, full width container that can be used to communicate short snippets of information to users. Banners are un-intrusive, non-dismissible, and only support link buttons.
  </Text>
  <Text class="pf-u-mb-md">
    See the <a target="_blank" href="https://www.patternfly.org/v4/components/banner/design-guidelines">PatternFly design guidelines</a> for more details.
  </Text>
</TextContent>

